snippet.title: Innawoods Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
INNAWOODS is a first person survival game made in 48 hours for a self imposed game jam.

In order to survive you need to hunt animals for food, seek out water supplies, and scavange ammo from fallen enemies.

INNAWOODS supports both single and multiplayer modes, where you can take on the woods on your own or join with a group of friends.

INNAWOODS was created in 48 hours and as such may contain all sorts of hilarious bugs and glitches such as foxes attempting to climb up trees. If you come across anything noteworthy please leave a comment so I can fix it up.

Grab it on Gamejolt:
http://gamejolt.com/games/other/innawoods/11484/
